entries.title: US warns of expanding Iran, Russia defence ‘partnership’
entries.description: Washington accuses Moscow of offering Tehran 'an unprecedented level of military and technical support'.

entries.title: Photos: Messi’s Argentina defeat Netherlands in shootout
entries.description: Lionel Messi’s quest to win the World Cup moves into semifinals after Argentina beat the Netherlands 4-3 on penalties.

entries.title: Recap: Netherlands vs Argentina – World Cup 2022
entries.description: Argentina win 4-3 on penalties after Netherlands had come back from two goals down to equalise in normal time.
